column5: Hi,Has anyone out there ever been to Thicket Wood lake. It is one of Canadian Fly-in fishings outpost camps. I'm going in June so I trying to get some info.Thanks,Robby

we went to thicketwood about 3 years ago and did great caught all the eyes we wanted they have a very nice cabin and good boats I would go back again the only thing i dont like is you have to go for a weekany other questions feel free to email me rick
